B.lY=new A.n6("Experience","Through my experiences as a Flutter developer at Herfa Mirotech and Obtulus, I've gained valuable insights into the world of mobile and desktop application development. My proficiency in Flutter, Dart, Firebase, and desktop application development has been instrumental in crafting solutions that meet the needs of various projects, including Plaza Food Delivery and Breezy Mood Food Delivery.",null)
B.lZ=new A.n6("Education","I attended the preparatory class at the National Polytechnic School of Algiers, where I delved deep into foundational concepts in mathematics, physics, and engineering. This rigorous program laid the groundwork for my academic journey in electrical engineering at The Higher School of Industrial Technologies in Annaba. Throughout my studies, I immersed myself in subjects like circuit theory, electromagnetism, and signal processing, developing a strong theoretical understanding alongside practical skills. My time at both institutions instilled in me a passion for problem-solving and a commitment to excellence in engineering.",null)
B.m_=new A.n6("About Me","I am a motivated individual with a passion for software development, especially making mobile apps. Working as a Flutter developer at Herfa Mirotech and Obtulus team has made me even more excited about creating innovative solutions. Now, I am eagerly seeking new opportunities where I can continue to grow professionally, contribute to exciting projects, and collaborate with talented teams. With a strong foundation in Flutter, Dart, Firebase, and I`m ready for new challenges.",null)
B.m0=new A.n6("Contact","Hey! I appreciate you looking at my public profile. Please feel free to ask me anything or to discuss anything with me. I'm happy to chat with and meet new people. Regardless of the fact that I don't use social media much, you can find me there. So find me and get in touch with me. Send me an email if you need to discuss anything serious with me. I'll get back to you in 12 to 24 hours.",null)
